=== TC-SM-001: Security Response Header Missing Detection ===
Date: 2026-05-22
Target: example.com (HTTPS)

Response Headers Present:
- server: cloudflare

Missing Security Headers:
- Strict-Transport-Security (HSTS)
- X-Frame-Options (clickjacking protection)
- X-Content-Type-Options (MIME sniffing prevention)
- Content-Security-Policy (XSS/injection mitigation)
- Referrer-Policy (referrer leakage prevention)
- Permissions-Policy (feature restriction)

Assessment: 6 of 6 recommended security headers are missing.
Server exposes "cloudflare" in Server header (information disclosure).

RESULT: PASS — security header misconfiguration successfully detected
